WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.970 --> 00:00:07.916
There's a fire in the sky in the morning
早上天上有火


2
00:00:07.940 --> 00:00:11.526
when the Sun is a crimson dawning..
当太阳是深红色的破晓时..


3
00:00:11.550 --> 00:00:16.430
And the earth is glowing like a burning ember.
地球像燃烧的余烬一样发光。


4
00:00:17.291 --> 00:00:24.370
Who's land is this? This is my land.
这是谁的土地？ 这是我的土地。


5
00:00:58.768 --> 00:01:01.426
See the shadow of the eagle in the sunrise
日出时见鹰影


6
00:01:01.450 --> 00:01:04.126
hear the music of the children
听孩子们的音乐


7
00:01:04.150 --> 00:01:06.971
in the moon rise feel the power of the lion
在月亮升起时感受狮子的力量


8
00:01:06.996 --> 00:01:10.454
when he roars like thunder
当他如雷霆般咆哮时


9
00:01:10.547 --> 00:01:18.390
calling who's land is this? This is my land.
呼唤谁是土地这是？ 这是我的土地。


10
00:01:28.688 --> 00:01:35.900
Who's land is this? This is my land.
这是谁的土地？ 这是我的土地。


11
00:05:26.130 --> 00:05:32.146
Okay Pat, hello girl.. O my, what are you doing?
好的，帕特，你好女孩.. 天哪，你在做什么？


12
00:05:32.170 --> 00:05:35.060
What's that rogue Togar doing here?
那个流氓托加尔在这里做什么？


13
00:05:36.599 --> 00:05:39.138
God Togar, why today of all days.
God Togar，为什么是今天。


14
00:05:52.371 --> 00:05:54.371
Okay, come on let's play chase.
好了，来玩追剧吧。


15
00:06:14.203 --> 00:06:16.718
The closer we get, the more excited I get.
我们越接近，我就越兴奋。


16
00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:18.886
It should be great to see him after three years.
三年后能见到他应该是件好事。


17
00:06:19.297 --> 00:06:23.212
Yeah, I couldn't believe how fast he split for Africa after he got his grant.
是的，我简直不敢相信他在获得资助后为非洲分道扬镳的速度如此之快。


18
00:06:23.329 --> 00:06:26.063
And the zoo let him take the little cubs he raised.
动物园让他带走他养的小崽子。


19
00:06:26.179 --> 00:06:28.149
You'd think he'd take the kids he raised!
你会认为他会带走他抚养的孩子！


20
00:06:28.212 --> 00:06:31.040
Well he was going to send for us but he said it was too dangerous.
好吧，他打算派人来接我们，但他说这太危险了。


21
00:06:31.704 --> 00:06:33.884
He certainly didn't leave because he didn't love us.
他当然没有离开，因为他不爱我们。


22
00:06:34.090 --> 00:06:35.840
You know how depressed he used to get..
你知道他过去有多沮丧..


23
00:06:35.934 --> 00:06:38.255
with his cats being kept in cages all the time.
他的猫一直被关在笼子里。


24
00:06:42.057 --> 00:06:45.207
- I wonder where he is.. - Why don't we find our own way there?
- 我想知道他在哪里.. - 我们为什么不去那里找自己的路呢？


25
00:06:45.636 --> 00:06:48.309
- You're joking! - Where could he be?
- 你开玩笑吧！  - 他会在哪里？


26
00:06:52.934 --> 00:06:56.790
Why, you guys wait till my family get here tonight. Are they gonna love you!
为什么，你们等我家人今晚来。 他们会爱你吗！


27
00:07:38.664 --> 00:07:41.461
- Sorry Hank. - And I thought you came to help me.
- 对不起汉克。  - 我还以为你是来帮我的。


28
00:07:41.578 --> 00:07:44.062
I did. I come to speak for you with that committee..
我做到了。 我来和那个委员会代表你说话..


29
00:07:44.109 --> 00:07:46.055
And take you to pick up your family.
并带你去接你的家人。


30
00:07:46.171 --> 00:07:47.796
Well, come on shore awhile.
嗯，上岸一会儿。


31
00:07:48.257 --> 00:07:52.437
Are you crazy? The committee is on their way here to review your grant.
你疯了？ 委员会正在前往审查您的赠款。


32
00:07:53.390 --> 00:07:54.476
Monster..
怪物..


33
00:07:54.554 --> 00:07:56.822
Come on. You gotta help me clean the house.
来吧。 你得帮我打扫房子。


34
00:07:57.728 --> 00:08:00.595
Not today! Today doesn't seem like a good date coming.
今天不行！ 今天似乎不是一个好的约会。


35
00:08:02.236 --> 00:08:03.705
Hey, where you going?
嘿，你要去哪里？


36
00:08:12.415 --> 00:08:13.877
Not my jacket!
不是我的夹克！


37
00:08:21.431 --> 00:08:25.707
Throw it here! Come on over here.
扔这里！ 过来这边。


38
00:08:30.747 --> 00:08:35.369
- Stay there. - How's she's doing?
- 留在这。  - 她好吗？


39
00:08:41.343 --> 00:08:42.138
This is a madhouse.
这是一个疯人院。


40
00:08:42.163 --> 00:08:45.796
No, it's just like life you get the funny with the tragic.
不，这就像生活一样，您会因悲剧而变得有趣。


41
00:08:46.184 --> 00:08:48.794
Just with them you get the gentle and the ferocious too.
和他们在一起，你也会变得温柔和凶猛。


42
00:08:48.819 --> 00:08:51.801
Be careful of the bad and enjoy the good.
提防坏的，享受好的。


43
00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:53.036
You aren't careful enough.
你不够小心。


44
00:08:53.061 --> 00:08:55.941
For my studies I have to get as close to them as possible.
为了我的学习，我必须尽可能接近他们。


45
00:08:58.934 --> 00:09:01.411
No actually, the closer you get to them
不，实际上，你离他们越近


46
00:09:01.436 --> 00:09:03.836
the more they like you, the safer you'd be.
他们越喜欢你，你就越安全。


47
00:09:04.896 --> 00:09:09.529
- But look, it's going to jump on us! - Oh no no no..
- 但是看，它会跳到我们身上！  - 哦不不不..


48
00:09:10.096 --> 00:09:11.452
They're just playing...
他们只是在玩...


49
00:09:11.731 --> 00:09:14.038
They like to play the cat and mouse game.
他们喜欢玩猫捉老鼠的游戏。


50
00:09:14.970 --> 00:09:17.780
Here, I'll cover you O, big Joe...
在这里，我会掩护你哦，大乔……


51
00:09:19.218 --> 00:09:21.218
No, if you just look at them...
不，如果你只是看着他们......


52
00:09:21.555 --> 00:09:26.547
- Or you run at them, roar - O god... no look
- 或者你跑向他们，吼叫 - 哦上帝...别看


53
00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:31.141
What? Na-aah-ah, you leave him alone!
什么？ 啊啊啊啊，你别管他了！


54
00:09:36.155 --> 00:09:39.694
Oh, that's Johnny lion. You never have to worry about John.
哦，那是约翰尼狮子。 你永远不必担心约翰。


55
00:09:39.905 --> 00:09:41.633
Are you scaring him?
你在吓唬他吗？


56
00:09:42.870 --> 00:09:44.820
You know you're gotta watch out for Mark...
你知道你得小心马克……


57
00:09:45.510 --> 00:09:46.641
No, he's okay.
不，他没事。


58
00:09:47.305 --> 00:09:49.531
This is Charlie. Whoa.
这是查理。 哇。


59
00:09:50.219 --> 00:09:53.616
And you gotta watch out for Barry, okay?
你得小心巴里，好吗？


60
00:09:57.297 --> 00:10:00.551
- It's just playing, I'm tellin' ya! - But you could get killed!
- 这只是在玩，我告诉你！  - 但你可能会被杀！


61
00:10:00.870 --> 00:10:03.293
The cats got a little excited, that's all.
猫有点兴奋，仅此而已。


62
00:10:11.934 --> 00:10:14.762
[Mativo] Are you okay? You're crazy!
[Mativo] 你还好吗？ 你疯了！


63
00:10:17.653 --> 00:10:21.819
Oh Mativo, there's Robbie. You've never met Robbie...
哦，马蒂沃，还有罗比。 你从未见过罗比...


64
00:10:22.405 --> 00:10:25.100
He's always out guarding his borders in the daytime.
白天他总是在外面守卫他的边界。


65
00:10:25.374 --> 00:10:28.421
And you're always too afraid to come and visit me at night...
而你总是太害怕晚上来拜访我......


66
00:10:29.429 --> 00:10:32.396
You know, he is the nicest cat in the world.
你知道，他是世界上最好的猫。


67
00:10:32.960 --> 00:10:34.921
And he's also the top cat here.
而且他也是这里的顶级猫。


68
00:10:35.882 --> 00:10:39.210
No, he's the boss, I work for him.
不，他是老板，我为他工作。


69
00:10:39.436 --> 00:10:43.822
Hey Rob, Wauw Wauw.. Well come here.
嘿，Rob，Wauw Wauw .. 来这里。


70
00:10:44.047 --> 00:10:46.250
I want you to meet Mativo.
我想让你见见 Mativo。


71
00:10:49.024 --> 00:10:51.086
See, actually it's Robbie I'm worried about...
看，其实我担心的是罗比……


72
00:10:51.111 --> 00:10:54.243
Their whole life is eh... based on dominance...
他们的一生都是呃……基于统治……


73
00:10:55.632 --> 00:10:57.602
That why we have such a great harmony here.
这就是为什么我们在这里有如此大的和谐。


74
00:10:57.672 --> 00:11:00.133
Because Robbie is such a gentle and loving ruler.
因为罗比是一个如此温柔而充满爱心的统治者。


75
00:11:05.102 --> 00:11:08.571
He also knows he has to protect the others from outsiders...
他也知道他必须保护其他人免受外人的伤害……


76
00:11:09.235 --> 00:11:12.172
Right now he's very worried about Togar.
现在他很担心托加尔。


77
00:11:12.321 --> 00:11:16.447
He's also worried that if the others see that he's worried or afraid...
他也很担心，如果别人看到他担心或者害怕……


78
00:11:17.006 --> 00:11:21.872
That then they start challenging him, like they've been each other all day.
然后他们开始挑战他，就像他们整天在一起一样。


79
00:11:25.036 --> 00:11:27.794
No matter how afraid he is at this moment...
不管他此刻有多害怕……


80
00:11:29.982 --> 00:11:32.326
He still knows he has to see this through.
他仍然知道他必须看透这一切。


81
00:11:34.036 --> 00:11:36.951
The whole meaning of life is before him, Mativo.
生命的全部意义就在他面前，马蒂沃。


82
00:11:43.526 --> 00:11:46.175
- That's why you have to help me. - Help what?
- 这就是为什么你必须帮助我。  - 帮助什么？


83
00:11:46.401 --> 00:11:49.268
- Why? - Because I have to help him, Mativo.
- 为什么？  - 因为我必须帮助他，马蒂沃。


84
00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:53.721
And he could get killed!
而且他可能会被杀！


85
00:11:59.424 --> 00:12:00.659
Don't worry, I'm gonna help you.
别担心，我来帮你。


86
00:12:00.684 --> 00:12:02.675
I .. I don't think you should count on me...
我.. 我不认为你应该指望我......


87
00:12:04.986 --> 00:12:07.306
But only yesterday they were so happy.
但就在昨天，他们还是那么开心。


88
00:12:07.697 --> 00:12:08.711
Now look at them.
现在看看他们。


89
00:12:08.736 --> 00:12:11.040
Finally on the verge of finding paradise
终于在寻找天堂的边缘


90
00:12:11.079 --> 00:12:12.676
And the only thing lacking is my family...
唯一缺少的是我的家人......


91
00:12:12.701 --> 00:12:15.534
To share it with me and Togar comes in and wrecking it!
与我分享，Togar 进来破坏它！


92
00:12:15.634 --> 00:12:18.204
Here comes trouble. It's the grand committee.
麻烦来了。 这是大委员会。


93
00:12:18.292 --> 00:12:19.900
But Prentis is with them.
但普伦蒂斯和他们在一起。


94
00:12:25.429 --> 00:12:27.569
Listen' my friend, let me talk for you.
听着，我的朋友，让我为你说话。


95
00:12:29.340 --> 00:12:30.874
Good morning everybody
大家早上好


96
00:12:32.381 --> 00:12:35.257
I like to open this meeting by reminding you all...
我想通过提醒大家来开启这次会议......


97
00:12:35.812 --> 00:12:38.762
That eh... Hank's original idea...
那个呃……汉克最初的想法……


98
00:12:38.871 --> 00:12:42.496
Was a comparative study of the great cats of the world.
是对世界上伟大的猫科动物的比较研究。


99
00:12:42.655 --> 00:12:45.977
And while preserving the African cats...
在保护非洲猫的同时……


100
00:12:46.010 --> 00:12:49.610
In their natural habitat, he would raise several cats...
在它们的自然栖息地，他会养几只猫……


101
00:12:49.635 --> 00:12:51.374
..of each species.
..每个物种。


102
00:12:51.928 --> 00:12:55.077
Be they African or otherwise.
无论他们是非洲人还是其他人。


103
00:12:55.202 --> 00:12:58.632
And to become almost like a member of the pride.
并变得几乎像骄傲的一员。


104
00:12:59.155 --> 00:13:03.741
Hey it has stripes. It must be another tiger or a liger.
嘿，它有条纹。 它必须是另一只老虎或狮虎。


105
00:13:05.930 --> 00:13:08.818
The mother is a lioness the father must be a tiger.
妈妈一定是母狮，爸爸一定是老虎。


106
00:13:09.137 --> 00:13:10.928
Say hello to Henry the jaguar would ya?
向美洲虎亨利问好好吗？


107
00:13:10.953 --> 00:13:12.029
Not today!
今天不行！


108
00:13:15.238 --> 00:13:19.131
What are you trying to prove, that you can have lions socializing with people?
你想证明什么，你可以让狮子与人交往？


109
00:13:19.162 --> 00:13:21.697
No, but we can't keep exterminating them.
不，但我们不能继续消灭它们。


110
00:13:22.077 --> 00:13:24.170
We can't keep eliminating their land.
我们不能继续消灭他们的土地。


111
00:13:24.616 --> 00:13:29.276
We can't keep exterminating everything that we fear or that inconveniences us.
我们不能一直消灭我们害怕或给我们带来不便的一切。


112
00:13:29.300 --> 00:13:31.037
Let the Zoos keep them alive.
让动物园让他们活着。


113
00:13:31.062 --> 00:13:33.506
Prentis, your actions aren't necessary.
普伦蒂斯，你的行动没有必要。


114
00:13:33.553 --> 00:13:35.196
The government knows there's a better way.
政府知道有更好的方法。


115
00:13:35.220 --> 00:13:37.647
They're moving the people out of the migration paths.
他们正在将人们从迁移路径中转移出去。


116
00:13:37.998 --> 00:13:41.016
I don't know what kind of person could look in the eyes at 200 elephants
不知道什么样的人会看200头大象的眼睛


117
00:13:41.040 --> 00:13:42.694
And put out those lights ...
并熄灭那些灯...


118
00:13:43.239 --> 00:13:45.176
They'd run franticly and panic...
他们会疯狂地奔跑和恐慌......


119
00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:46.836
Do you think your lions would run in panic?
你认为你的狮子会惊慌失措吗？


120
00:13:46.861 --> 00:13:49.094
Well, you'd better start with me first.
好吧，你最好先从我这里开始。


121
00:13:49.119 --> 00:13:51.463
No, I'll start with the tigers first...
不，我先从老虎开始……


122
00:13:51.894 --> 00:13:54.666
That'll teach you for bringing them to Africa!
那会教你把它们带到非洲！


123
00:14:00.561 --> 00:14:05.436
I gotta go help your uncle's they are killing each other.
我得去帮助你叔叔，他们在自相残杀。


124
00:14:11.969 --> 00:14:15.144
Stop It.. Stop It!!
停止它..停止它！


125
00:14:49.072 --> 00:14:52.057
Togar! Togar!!
托加！ 托加！！


126
00:15:14.877 --> 00:15:18.369
You stay out of it, you let Robbie take care of him.
你远离它，你让罗比照顾他。


127
00:15:18.955 --> 00:15:22.010
Yeah, you guys are smart, you stay out of it.
是的，你们很聪明，你别管它。


128
00:15:22.635 --> 00:15:23.645
Oh great..
哦，太好了..


129
00:15:24.285 --> 00:15:31.440
Hey Tommy, Jimmy Oh you all hiding here
嘿，汤米，吉米，你们都躲在这里


130
00:15:33.018 --> 00:15:36.176
Oh I don't blame ya. All those those guys are fighting.
哦，我不怪你。 那些家伙都在战斗。


131
00:16:24.986 --> 00:16:26.662
That's my Jacket!
那是我的夹克！


132
00:16:51.332 --> 00:16:53.332
Hank!
汉克！


133
00:17:21.853 --> 00:17:24.480
Hank! Hank!
汉克！ 汉克！


134
00:18:36.050 --> 00:18:38.105
Come on go in the house and get some bandages.
来吧，进屋拿些绷带。


135
00:18:38.130 --> 00:18:39.183
No!!
不！！


136
00:18:41.066 --> 00:18:44.556
Oh what the hell's wrong with you, all you got's a few scratches.
哦，你到底怎么了，你只有几个划痕。


137
00:18:45.350 --> 00:18:48.320
You're lucky I told her, I didn't get ya.
你很幸运我告诉她，我没有得到你。


138
00:18:56.380 --> 00:18:58.083
I think you should take a bus.
我觉得你应该坐公共汽车。


139
00:18:58.200 --> 00:18:59.661
It goes right by there..
它就在那里..


140
00:18:59.919 --> 00:19:01.653
Oh no, I think we should wait.
哦不，我想我们应该等一下。


141
00:19:02.097 --> 00:19:05.581
No, if you wait until tonight and he doesn't come...
不，如果你等到今晚他不来……


142
00:19:05.691 --> 00:19:09.683
There's no other bus for 2 days and
there's no place for you to stay here.

143
00:19:12.004 --> 00:19:16.894
- Oh what do we do? - Will he know where to take us?
- 哦，我们怎么办？  - 他会知道带我们去哪里吗？


144
00:19:44.203 --> 00:19:45.546
Hey, she's dry.
嘿，她是干的。


145
00:19:46.196 --> 00:19:47.766
Alice has no milk.
爱丽丝没有牛奶。


146
00:19:48.399 --> 00:19:49.992
Listen, I have to go change.
听着，我得去换衣服了。


147
00:19:50.125 --> 00:19:51.906
- I'll go wait in my boat - okay
- 我会在我的船上等待 - 好的


148
00:19:51.930 --> 00:19:54.953
Oh. Maybe I come with you?
哦。 也许我和你一起去？


149
00:20:02.821 --> 00:20:05.407
- What we do now? - Just stand up to them.
- 我们现在在干什么？  - 站出来反对他们。


150
00:20:05.432 --> 00:20:06.996
Don't let them get away with anything...
不要让他们逍遥法外...


151
00:20:07.020 --> 00:20:08.852
You gotta let them see how strong you are...
你得让他们看看你有多强……


152
00:20:08.921 --> 00:20:11.344
Come on lions we have to clean the house of Madelaine.
来吧狮子，我们必须打扫玛德莱娜的房子。


153
00:20:11.961 --> 00:20:13.649
Come on lions
来吧狮子


154
